result.content: Hello bookworms frum all over the wrld! Im writing 2 share with u som great books ive just discovered omg. It is a rly beautiful n touching story bout friendship n ofc luv n partnership n family and during reading i felt like a part of the book it was amazing i was shocked af but it isnt all! The book has many pictures so u dont hav 2 imagine everything by urself so u dont feel like ur in school again thank God! U think tht this is the end? Ofc no cause the main character has truly beautiful name im sure u ll fall in luv with him well i started reading because of his name cause as u know frum my blog im the biggest fan of our new president Donld the Duck so i want 2 know everything bout him!! Well i didnt know tht hes so old cause the books im reading are old i dont know what 2 think bout tht how could he be my man when hes so old okay Daisy take him i wont be jeallous. How bout u my dear followers? Hav u read books bout our new president? Let me know! PEACE N LUV XOXOXOXOXOOXOXOXO
